ENGLISH: Movement skill that allows the Mecha-Suit to teleport instantly anywhere within the line of sight and then to attack with a kinetic shockwave dealing Area damage which harms even tough enemies.

ENGLISH: The aim of this research is to combine Attack Teleport and Emergency Teleport to release a kinetic shockwave dealing Area damage before and after teleporting the very short distance through the Rift field.
